item.title: Cotton Bucket Hat
item.dc:creator: phulethanhdung
item.description: The Iconic Silhouette He garments labelled as Committed are products that have been produced using sustainable fibers or processes, reducing their environmental impact. Mango’s goal is to support the implementation of practices more committed to the environment, and therefore increase the number of sustainable garments in the collection.
